"Funktionen :c:func:`PyErr_NewException` kan skapa en klass med "
"basklassen :exc:`Exception` (om inte en annan klass anges istûÊllet fûÑr "
"``NULL``), som beskrivs i :ref:`bltin-exceptions`."

#: ../../extending/extending.rst:264
msgid ""
"Note also that the :c:data:`!SpamError` variable retains a reference to the "
"newly created exception class; this is intentional!  Since the exception "
"could be removed from the module by external code, an owned reference to the "
"class is needed to ensure that it will not be discarded, causing :c:data:`!"
"SpamError` to become a dangling pointer. Should it become a dangling "
"pointer, C code which raises the exception could cause a core dump or other "
"unintended side effects."
msgstr ""
"Notera ocksûË att variabeln :c:data:`!SpamError` behûËller en referens till "
"den nyskapade undantagsklassen; detta ûÊr avsiktligt!  Eftersom undantaget "
"kan tas bort frûËn modulen av extern kod, behûÑvs en ûÊgd referens till klassen "
"fûÑr att sûÊkerstûÊlla att den inte kasseras, vilket gûÑr att :c:data:`!"
"SpamError` blir en dinglande pekare. Om den blir en dinglande pekare kan C-"
"kod som vûÊcker undantaget orsaka en kûÊrndump eller andra oavsiktliga "
"bieffekter."

#: ../../extending/extending.rst:271
msgid ""
"For now, the :c:func:`Py_DECREF` call to remove this reference is missing. "
"Even when the Python interpreter shuts down, the global :c:data:`!SpamError` "
"variable will not be garbage-collected. It will \"leak\". We did, however, "
"ensure that this will happen at most once per process."
msgstr ""
"FûÑr tillfûÊllet saknas :c:func:`Py_DECREF`-anropet fûÑr att ta bort denna "
"referens. ûven nûÊr Python-tolken stûÊngs av kommer den globala :c:data:`!"
"SpamError`-variabeln inte att samlas in. Den kommer att \"lûÊcka\". Vi har "
"dock fûÑrsûÊkrat oss om att detta kommer att ske hûÑgst en gûËng per process."

#: ../../extending/extending.rst:276
msgid ""
"We discuss the use of :c:macro:`PyMODINIT_FUNC` as a function return type "
"later in this sample."
msgstr ""
"Vi diskuterar anvûÊndningen av :c:macro:`PyMODINIT_FUNC` som funktionens "
"returtyp senare i detta exempel."

#: ../../extending/extending.rst:279
