#: ../../extending/extending.rst:833
msgid "PyObject *Py_BuildValue(const char *format, ...);"
msgstr "PyObject *Py_BuildValue(const char *format, ...);"

#: ../../extending/extending.rst:835
msgid ""
"It recognizes a set of format units similar to the ones recognized "
"by :c:func:`PyArg_ParseTuple`, but the arguments (which are input to the "
"function, not output) must not be pointers, just values.  It returns a new "
"Python object, suitable for returning from a C function called from Python."
msgstr ""
"Den kûÊnner igen en uppsûÊttning formatenheter som liknar dem som kûÊnns igen "
"av :c:func:`PyArg_ParseTuple`, men argumenten (som ûÊr indata till "
"funktionen, inte utdata) fûËr inte vara pekare, bara vûÊrden.  Den returnerar "
"ett nytt Python-objekt, lûÊmpligt fûÑr att returnera frûËn en C-funktion som "
"anropas frûËn Python."

#: ../../extending/extending.rst:840
msgid ""
"One difference with :c:func:`PyArg_ParseTuple`: while the latter requires "
"its first argument to be a tuple (since Python argument lists are always "
"represented as tuples internally), :c:func:`Py_BuildValue` does not always "
"build a tuple.  It builds a tuple only if its format string contains two or "
"more format units. If the format string is empty, it returns ``None``; if it "
"contains exactly one format unit, it returns whatever object is described by "
"that format unit.  To force it to return a tuple of size 0 or one, "
"parenthesize the format string."
msgstr ""
"En skillnad med :c:func:`PyArg_ParseTuple`: medan den senare krûÊver att dess "
"fûÑrsta argument ûÊr en tupel (eftersom Python-argumentlistor alltid "
"representeras som tuplar internt), bygger :c:func:`Py_BuildValue` inte "
"alltid en tupel.  Den bygger en tupel endast om dess formatstrûÊng innehûËller "
"tvûË eller fler formatenheter. Om formatstrûÊngen ûÊr tom returnerar den "
"``None``; om den innehûËller exakt en formatenhet returnerar den det objekt "
"som beskrivs av den formatenheten.  Om du vill tvinga den att returnera en "
"tupel av storlek 0 eller ett, sûÊtter du formatstrûÊngen i parentes."

